reviewText: This movie would have been okay if it tied all of the scenes together.  Too many characters injected into the movie for no good reason.
Qulity was not good but i like it bought it because Diane Sands was in it plus i like the name HONEY BABY LOL!!!!!

I bought this DVD only because of Diana Sanda and the late Calvin Lockhart. The video is not of great quality, nor is the sound.

I found myself falling to sleep, twice.
